<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV99">
<l>īṉaccol lāyiṉu māka veṟitirai vaiyamuṟṟu</l>
<l>mēṉat turuvā yiṭantapi rāṉiruṅ kaṟpakañcēr</l>
<l>vāṉat tavarkkumal lātavark kumaṟṟel lāyavarkkuñ</l>
<l>ñāṉap pirāṉaiyal lālillai nāṉkaṇṭa nallatuvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if there be word of degradation, let it be. For those in heaven,</l>
<l>those who are not and all others, who join the big wishfulfilling tree,</l>
<l>the lord who dug out, in the form of a hog, the whole world [bordered by the sea with]</l>
<l>dashing waves nothing good is there seen by me besides the lord of knowledge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
